            <title>[LU-16125] Make sanity-sec more robust with SSK</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16125</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Encryption related tests in sanity-sec carry out unmount and mount of clients in order to exercise code with and without the encryption key. In case SSK is in use (&lt;tt&gt;SHARED_KEY=true&lt;/tt&gt;), we need to make sure flavors are properly applied before carrying on.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
